# Hooks

## Basic Requirements
- Hook names must start with `use`; encapsulate one responsibility
- Accept typed inputs; return stable shapes; minimize re-renders via memoization

## Mandatory Actions
- Expose loading/error/data tri-state; support cancellation
- Provide dependency arrays and document assumptions for effects
- Use state machines or reducers when branching grows

## Forbidden Behaviors
- Conditionally calling hooks; returning non-deterministic shapes
- Hidden network requests without clear API

